target: You're very welcome. Thank you for using Cambridge TownInfo centre.
context: <user> Hi! Can you tell me what trains are available on Friday after 18:30? <system> Certainly, but first I need to know where you are departing from and what your destination is. <user> I'm going from Stevenage to Cambridge. <system> The first train after 18:30 is TR4969, which leaves at 19:54. Would you like a ticket, or more information? <user> Yes I would like to book it for 8 people and I will need the reference number. <system> Sure, I have booked your tickets for 8 people, your reference number is : T6B9UNBQ . <user> Thank you for all your help, that's all I needed today. <system>
